  "title": "Class LogLevelFilter",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Filters.LogLevelFilter' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Filters.LogLevelFilter' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Filters_LogLevelFilter'>Class LogLevelFilter    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Filters/LogLevelFilter.cs#L39'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Filters.html'>Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Filters</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Filters.LogLevelFilter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Filters log entries based on their severity level.\nOnly entries with level &gt;= minimum level pass through.\nAOT-compatible: Simple value comparison.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public sealed class LogLevelFilter : ILogFilter</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Inheritance</h4><dl class=\"typelist inheritance\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Filters.LogLevelFilter.html'>LogLevelFilter</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Implements</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogFilter.html'>ILogFilter</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Inherited Members</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object)'>object.Equals(object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object-system-object)'>object.Equals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gethashcode'>object.GetHashCode()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='htt